    {
        "url": "/quotes/paul_bloom_644631",
        "quote": "Some scholars argue that although the brain might contain neural subsystems, or modules, specialized for tasks like recognizing faces and understanding language, it also contains a part that constitutes a person, a self: the chief executive of all the subsystems.",
