    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/paul_bloom_644634",
        "quote": "We benefit, intellectually and personally, from the interplay between different selves, from the balance between long-term contemplation and short-term impulse. We should be wary about tipping the scales too far. The community of selves shouldn't be a democracy, but it shouldn't be a dictatorship, either.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Paul Bloom",
            "url": "/quotes/paul_bloom_644634"
